	Alexander Bieber
	---


Hide the menu-bar for certain paths. 

	Sometimes you want to hide the menu-bar for certain paths, the index-file for example. 
	To do so add a <custom> tag to the site.xml and configure a <hideMenu> element as follows: 
    
--------------------------
<project>
  ...
  <custom>
    ...
    <hideMenu>
      <path>index.html</path>
    </hideMenu>
    ...
  </custom>
  ...
</project>
--------------------------

